Welcome to the **Image Steganography & Visualization Toolkit** ‚Äî a comprehensive and modular Python-based project that enables secure message encoding into images, 
and provides tools for analyzing, visualizing, and understanding the impact of such techniques using computer vision and deep learning.

üöÄ How to Run
# Encode or decode messages
python code/steganography_lsb.py

# Visualize image difference heatmap
